A penetration tester injected javascript onto our page.

Avoid html_safe
Do not use html_safe on user-generated content unless you are 100% sure the data has been sanitized. For example:

Validate and Sanitize Inputs
Validate input data in models or controllers to ensure only expected data is processed.
Use gems like Loofah or Sanitize for more granular HTML sanitization.